Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}支援大家进行严酷的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以自己的方式努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和同伴们建立了信赖关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我原本是这么想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说得太突然 我不太能理解状况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这该不会是整人之类…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亚利欧斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们是…认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请 请告诉我理由!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}理由?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}理由只有一个不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为你是绊脚石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你完全没有派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}会扯大家后腿的存在就是累赘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}累赘…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你心里也有数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没办法给敌人像样的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反而给同伴添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能办到的事不过就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}驱使动物进行探索和搬运行李而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不叫没用什么才叫没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.18,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本来就是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.60,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让小孩跟着我们也很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这到底是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说到底我本来就反对让驭兽使成为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我原本期待就算只是小石子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我的照耀之下也能绽放一些光芒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亚利欧斯真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}糟蹋像勇者亚利欧斯这样尊贵慈悲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来我一直都是被同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.20,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}糟蹋像勇者亚利欧斯这样尊贵慈悲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么看待的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.57,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才是他的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么会…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别再继续让我们失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对了 要把装备留下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为那是我们收集的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么终于要攻略迷途之森了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.05,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总算是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这宽广空无一物的乡下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}停留了好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都是绊脚石调度物资花太多时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是对他有些许期待的我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就当成是段不错的休养时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此 这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}累赘在最后也派上些用场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.53,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我感觉和同伴完全断绝了缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}终究只是个瘦弱的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你身为勇者队伍一员的自觉和实力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你什么时候才可以派上打杂以外的用场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的是个杂鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家别这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因他也努力到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过是以驭兽使来说就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在旅程中大家对我有点刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我原本以为是因为对我有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我或许从一开始就没有被当成同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 比起那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这之后该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目的 装备还有旅费全都失去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勇者大人那边的工作结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 其实我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}表演一下平常的那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}表演一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}表演 表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.20,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暂时契约完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我之前也有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为这是暂时的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然很简单就能缔结契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但能使役的时间也相对较短
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看来对大家来说还有点难理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因哥哥果然好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我以后要成为驭兽使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们之前不是说要成为勇者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为勇者大人他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要我们平民一接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就会露出很厌恶的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遇到贵族和有钱人却会摆出好脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感觉真的很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来亚利欧斯他们的评价这么差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}难怪调度物资的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}商店的人都不太情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但雷因哥哥就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都会和我们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}越来越难说出被开除的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}干脆去当冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去各种地方闯荡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后一获千金!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}千金!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}冒险者…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如候鸟般生活 自由地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了报酬接受委托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以一己之力生存的冒险者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对刚失去打倒魔王这个目的的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或许正适合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欢迎来到冒险者公会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是负责柜台的娜塔莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接着为你说明冒险者测验…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之前可以详细地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有关冒险者的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}说来惭愧  其实我不是特别清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为亚利欧斯他们瞧不起冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以没有什么交集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有很多志愿者都瞧不起基础说明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像你这样会有很好的评价哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么就容我说明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先冒险者和魔物相同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有着S到F的等级…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有其他问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么关于冒险者测验
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个 你的职业是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就登记驭兽使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}驭兽使!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一个人没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为你是绊脚石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请千万不要勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}知难而退对冒险者也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你知道公会为什么要进行测验
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才能注册冒险者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果不成熟的冒险者不断让委托失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}会事关公会的信用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}答对了 回答得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果信用下降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}上层也不会坐视不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个先姑且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}测验内容「讨伐10只哥布林」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与「采集20把药草」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对委托多数为魔物讨伐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和药草采集的冒险者来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果无法达成这种最基本的委托的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}公会是不会承认对方的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就10只了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你帮我找哥布林啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但就算是驭兽使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是可以轻松赢过F级的哥布林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拿到哥布林的魔石了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再来只要采集药草拿到公会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惨叫?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从森林深处传来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}杀手虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等级D的魔物 杀手虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就连老练的冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一不小心也会失去性命的棘手存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然我是打不赢它的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那边的小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能动吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快趁现在逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有能驯服的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也没有能用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要争取让女孩子逃走的时间还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为 为什么还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至少要把最后的力气…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然一击就把那个杀手虎解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个世界上有着被称为最强种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是拥有超乎想象力量的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}龙族 圣灵族以及神族等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}存在着许多的最强种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但在其中也有称得上特别稀有的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}猫灵族?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经到…极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}肚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}肚?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是货真价实的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在最强种中据说濒临灭绝的猫灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然不能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但能强化到极限的肉体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在最强种中也是数一数二的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还以为就要那样饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还好我有带随身粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过是不是太夸张了点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才没有那种事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已经好几天没吃没喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都看见已经去天国的爷爷他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在向我招手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的不是能开玩笑的状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差点离灭绝又近了一步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的不是在开玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我还没自我介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如你所见是猫灵族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是雷因・舒拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在冒险者测验的途中遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是希望你能叫我奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那也叫我雷因就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还好是雷因救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏为什么会倒在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是 在这平凡无奇的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有濒临绝种的猫灵族出现很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是在旅行而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我们的个体数很少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一直隐居在深山里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我觉得这种生活有些无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以就踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后遇到雷因 被你所救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像是命运一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那接着告诉我有关雷因的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那雷因原本在勇者队伍是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 虽然只有半年左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原本光回想都觉得讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从来没和他人讲过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却能对奏全盘托出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个勇者不可原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然把雷因开除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因人明明那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是在为我生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为雷因救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏真是温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我碍手碍脚也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算留在那个队伍里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概也不会有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果雷因不在意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我也不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然还是有些耿耿于怀就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好了 一顺手就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像不讨厌的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是但是 我要订正一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因才不是派不上用场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不如说非常的厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是个驭兽使哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但那份才能非常优秀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因应该可以使役我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我在看到了雷因的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全身感觉就像是被电流流过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是雷因的话或许就能使役我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能使役我们猫灵族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在全世界也是屈指可数的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以雷因是很厉害的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我能使役猫灵族?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那种事我连想都没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我说 雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要使役我看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果能使役最强种的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那该会多令人安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要有最强种的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就也不会再遇到那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像是命运一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是因为她是最强种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是我想和奏的关系变得更亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道了 就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾名为雷因・舒拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}缔结崭新之契约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}于此连结因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}胸藏誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}心怀希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}掌握力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}汝之名为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果奏在这里回答自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}契约就会成立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果没有的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就结束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错 契约成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看看你的手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像出现了什么奇怪的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是我和奏缔结契约的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样我和奏就缔结了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是我和雷因羁绊的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}羁绊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奇怪 不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是我和奏羁绊的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后请多多指教了 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我才要请你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被称为最强种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是拥有超乎想象力量的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这个被勇者队伍开除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}失去了同伴和目的的驭兽使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就这样使役了最强种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是要回去镇上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之前得完成冒险者测验才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我看看 这附近的话一定有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兔子?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先订下暂时契约
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么能订契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接着请它的同伴们聚集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}简直就是毛茸茸天国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再来和它们全部订下暂时契约
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去寻找这附近生长的药草然后带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别和食物搞混吃掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵喵喵喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是怎么回事喵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然能同时驯服这么多动物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且还能执行复杂的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是那么让人吃惊的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很让人惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一般来说行暂时契约时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一名驭兽使对一只动物就已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且雷因已经使役了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该不能再驯服了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然说雷因是个厉害的驭兽使的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这种事果然还是不可能的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏懂的真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.59,0:23:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道有驭兽使能做到这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我的故乡大家都能办到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以驭兽使来说这很普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完全不普通啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底谁才超乎常理啊喵!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}下集 同伴
